==Acquisitions==

==Donations==
===12/2/2010: Classic Variable Inductors and Voltmeters===
Recently donated, a set of 2 classic Variable Inductors and 2 AC Voltmeters. Very classy looking. Inductors are housed in a 6" wooden cube with feet, perfect for workbench usage. AC Voltmeter is a 4" square panel-mount. '''UNTESTED'''

===12/2/2010: Nordac Vector Frequency Inverter and High Voltage Power Supply.===
Frequency Inverter has damage on circuit board, one blown hi-voltage capacitor and resulting damage to nearby board. Other capacitors and components may be salvageable. Power supply seems to be in good condition, but requires 520V AC and is '''UNTESTED'''.
[http://www.artisan-scientific.com/info/nordac_vector_user_manual.pdf Frequency Inverter Operations Manual]
